OL,3,CMan threatened to blow up apartment
OL,4,Cblock in 32-hour standoff, court hears
OL,6,FA man claiming to have a bomb held a
OL,7,Fstandoff with police lasting nearly
OL,8,Ftwo days as he threatened to blow up
OL,9,Fan apartment block, a court has heard.
OL,11,FYaqub Younis is accused of the
OL,12,Fstandoff at The Gateway in Sheffield
OL,13,Fin February last year.
OL,15,FAround 80 residents were evacuated and
OL,16,Ffeared for their safety after the 49-
OL,17,Fyear-old defendant is alleged to have
OL,18,Ffalsely claimed to be carrying guns
OL,19,Fand explosives.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
