FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1780672278
OL,3,CMan threatened to blow up apartment
OL,4,Cblock in 32-hour standoff, court hears
OL,6,FProsecutors opening the trial at
OL,7,FSheffield Crown Court on Wednesday
OL,8,Ftold the jury that Younis was
OL,9,Fultimately found to be lying, but was
OL,10,Fdiscovered to be carrying "a number of
OL,11,Fknives, including a meat cleaver,
OL,12,Fwhich he brandished from the window of
OL,13,Fthe flat".
OL,15,FYounis had been a resident at the flat
OL,16,Fat the time of the siege, and the
OL,17,Falarm was raised on the evening of
OL,18,FMonday, February 10, when a neighbour
OL,19,Fcalled the police claiming the
OL,20,Fdefendant "told them that he had
OL,21,Fgrenades and explosives".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1780672278
OL,3,CMan threatened to blow up apartment
OL,4,Cblock in 32-hour standoff, court hears
OL,6,FAnnabelle Darlow KC, prosecuting, told
OL,7,Fthe court how, that same evening,
OL,8,FYounis was seen throwing objects from
OL,9,Fthe 9th floor balcony, including a
OL,10,Fflat screen television and other
OL,11,Fhousehold items which had been lit on
OL,12,Ffire.
OL,14,FYounis is alleged to have told
OL,15,Farriving police officers, "I have
OL,16,Floads of guns and explosives, you need
OL,17,Fto leave. You need to get out."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1780672278
OL,3,CMan threatened to blow up apartment
OL,4,Cblock in 32-hour standoff, court hears
OL,6,FMs Darlow said Younis, "was asked if
OL,7,Fthere were other people present in his
OL,8,Fproperty and he said in response that
OL,9,Fthere were three other people inside
OL,10,Fwith him".
OL,12,FPolice deployed firearms officers to
OL,13,Fthe scene, leading to a standoff which
OL,14,Fwould ultimately go on into the next
OL,15,Fday and night lasting a total of 32
OL,16,Fhours.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1780672278
OL,3,CMan threatened to blow up apartment
OL,4,Cblock in 32-hour standoff, court hears
OL,6,FIn this time, Younis allegedly made
OL,7,Fmultiple claims, including that he was
OL,8,Fbeing watched by MI5 as part of a tax
OL,9,Finvestigation against him, and that he
OL,10,Fhad been the victim of an attempted
OL,11,Fassassination - claims which Ms Darlow
OL,12,Fsuggested were "simply fiction
OL,13,Fdesigned to distract attention and
OL,14,Fattempt to excuse his own wrongdoing".
OL,16,FThe ordeal reached its conclusion in
OL,17,Fthe early hours of Wednesday morning,
OL,18,FMs Darlow said, when an officer asked
OL,19,Fto use the toilet and colleagues
OL,20,Fapprehended Younis, using a taser and
OL,21,FPAVA spray.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1780672278
OL,3,CMan threatened to blow up apartment
OL,4,Cblock in 32-hour standoff, court hears
OL,6,FIn interview, the court heard he
OL,7,Fclaimed he had returned to his flat on
OL,8,Fthe day of the standoff, believing he
OL,9,Fwas being watched and was victim of an
OL,10,Fattempted assassination from two
OL,11,Frooftop snipers.
OL,13,FYounis denies communicating false
OL,14,Finformation with intent, intentionally
OL,15,For recklessly causing a public
OL,16,Fnuisance, affray and criminal damage
OL,17,Fto property.
OL,19,FThe trial continues.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
